Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# The Way She Flies 她的飛相
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 入場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:04.92,Intro,,0,0,0,,你好。\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.22,Intro,,0,0,0,,我，名叫 Phileo\NI, am Phileo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:10.56,Intro,,0,0,0,,我要給你演奏一首歌\NI'm going to play a song for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.56,0:00:12.86,Intro,,0,0,0,,有關那位敏捷，彩虹色的馬兒\Nabout the fast, rainbow-y horse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:16.09,Intro,,0,0,0,,但首先，我得邀請你加入我，\NBut first, I must ask you to join me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:19.13,Intro,,0,0,0,,一起到世上最豔麗的小馬聚會\Nat the world's most alluring pony convention
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.57,Intro,,0,0,0,,「Equestria 洛杉磯」\N"Equestria LA"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:22.50,Intro,,0,0,0,,就在今年(2013)的五月\Nhappening this May
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:26.44,Intro,,0,0,0,,也或許，你可能會更想給自己看看\NOr perhaps, you'd prefer to feast your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:29.31,Intro,,0,0,0,,我的搞笑時刻，跟「馬迷俱樂部」一起\Nupon my silly times with the Brony Clubhouse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:33.68,Intro,,0,0,0,,這是什麼！？\NWhat is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:39.18,Intro,,0,0,0,,噓...安靜點，甜心(西班牙文)\NShhhh, silencio mi amor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.55,0:00:41.59,Intro,,0,0,0,,這首歌並非由吉他開始，\NFor this song does not begin with a guitar,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:44.39,Intro,,0,0,0,,而是在那小小的黑膠機上\Nbut on the humble vinyl record
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:47.83,Intro,,0,0,0,,就比如說這邊這台\NMuch like this one here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.46,0:00:51.93,Intro,,0,0,0,,來吧，朋友們，\NCome with me my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:55.63,Intro,,0,0,0,,我們的冒險，啟程。\Nour journey beings.
Comment: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:01.71,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}來，我們學了什麼\NNow, what have we learned
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.71,0:01:03.08,Flutter,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}很多的控制\NLots of control
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:03.54,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}很好\NGood
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:04.88,Flutter,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}大聲尖叫\NScreaming and hollering
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:07.31,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}對，而最重要的是\NYes, and most importantly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:07.95,Flutter,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}熱情\NPassion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:08.55,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}嘿\NRight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:11.25,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}那現在你知道歡呼的元素\NSo now that you know the elements of a good cheer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:14.22,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}來，聽一個\Nlet's, hear one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}一...二...三...\N1... 2... 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,上！\NGO!
Comment: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一道紅色\NFlash of red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.21,0:01:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼神的她飛上天\Nthe spectral wonder takes flight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她很確定，她很堅定，她感覺很爽\Nand she's ready and she's steady and she's feelin' just right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她有熱情，有動力，有決心要贏\NShe got the passion, the drive, the tenacity to win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}而只要十秒她就能讓你頭昏眼花\Nand in 10 seconds flat she'll take your head for a spin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,天如火燒，彷彿漸漸變成一顆密桃\NSky is burnin' and it's turnin' to a tangerine peach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好像在海南島沙灘的太陽下山\Nlike a sun slowly settin' over Huntington Beach
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她的肚子裡有顆火\NShe's got a fire in her belly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:55.46,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,嘿！\NYep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛裡有火\Nfire in her eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:56.83,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,對！\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,超音速的步伐在空中留下火跡\Nsupersonic strut leaves a fire in the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,越發亮，變成溫暖的金光\NBrighten up to a warm and golden glow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.27,0:02:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他充滿你的從腳到頭\Nlet it fill you all up from your head to your toe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讓那太陽閃在你頭\Nlet that sun shine down on ya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都叫大聲點\Neverypony scream louder
Comment: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,七彩在天空中\N7 colors in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看他飛過天空\NWatch her dash on by
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,天堂被遮住\NThe heavens are covered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,被如此的景色\Nwith so many wonders
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛她的飛相\NI love the way she flies
Comment: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,## 間奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:34.70,Rainbow,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}吼，你要這樣給我喊加油？\NUrgh, you're gonna cheer for me like that?
